      "description": "Scripture of the Moon Elf slowly charges Estes with energy. When the energy reaches 100 stacks, Estes' next Basic Attack will become enhanced, dealing 250( +100% Total Physical Attack) (+150% Total Magic Power) (Magic Damage) to the target and 125( +50% Total Physical Attack) (+75% Total Magic Power) (Magic Damage) to nearby enemies, and slowing them by 60% for 1.5s.",
