      "iconName": "Scripture_of_the_Moon_Elf",
      "tips": "Code of Moon Elves, can charge energy and improves its basic attack dealing 450 magic damage. This basic attack will surely slow down its target. Also, it can make a splash damage dealing 225 magic damage towards nearby enemies.",
