    "skill1": {
      "name": "Moonlight Immersion",
      "description": "Estes restores 250( +110% Total Magic Power) HP to the target allied hero immediately and links himself with them for 3s, slowly restoring 325( +60% Total Magic Power) HP to the target. Linking with an allied hero will also increase Estes' Hybrid Defense by 20 and Movement Speed by 15%, as well as the energy charging speed of the Scripture of the Moon Elf. Being too far from the target will break the link.",
